Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.81,0:09:00.72,TEXT,NTP,0,0,0,,15-0 薩拉曼迪涅大人得分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:05.11,TEXT,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啦 我發太快了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.65,0:09:07.19,TEXT,NTP,0,0,0,,給你放點水~嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:13.67,TEXT,NTP,0,0,0,,不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.39,0:09:24.32,TEXT,NTP,0,0,0,,15-15
